---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Calculate Generated Profits — Evium Charging"
  description="Turn idle parking into a passive revenue stream. Evium's no-cost EV charging model generates real income for property owners — zero capital required."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-evium-dark pt-20">
    <!-- Background grid lines -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]"
      style="background-image: linear-gradient(#2DC856 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, #2DC856 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"
    ></div>

    <!-- Radial glow -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[900px] h-[600px] rounded-full opacity-10"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #2DC856 0%, transparent 70%);"
    ></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-evium-green/10 border border-evium-green/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-8">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green"></span>
          <span class="text-evium-green text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Revenue Intelligence</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-8">
          Your parking lot is<br />
          <span class="text-evium-green">already an asset.</span><br />
          Time it paid like one.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-12">
          EV charging infrastructure turns idle pavement into a recurring revenue stream. With Evium's no-cost model, your property earns passive income from day one — no capital investment, no operational overhead.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact/quote"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-evium-green text-evium-dark font-bold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-evium-green/90 transition-colors"
          >
            Get My Revenue Estimate
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#revenue-projection"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-white/20 text-white font-semibold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:border-evium-green/50 hover:text-evium-green transition-colors"
          >
            See Revenue Projections
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Stat strip -->
      <div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-white/10 grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-evium-green">500+</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">Chargers installed</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-evium-green">$0</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">Capital required (no-cost model)</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-evium-green">$126K</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">5-yr potential per fast charger</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-evium-green">100%</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-1">Rebates handled by Evium</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       THE REVENUE OPPORTUNITY
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-28 bg-evium-dark-light">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-evium-green font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">The Opportunity</p>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black leading-tight mb-6">
            EV drivers are paying customers. Every session generates revenue.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Unlike a bike rack or a park bench, an EV charging station collects real dollars every time it's used. As EV adoption accelerates nationally, utilization rates rise — and so does your return.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            This isn't a speculative amenity play. It's measurable infrastructure with a documented revenue curve, backed by Evium's network of 500+ deployed chargers and real-world utilization data from commercial properties across the Northeast and beyond.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5">
          <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-evium-green/15 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-1">Rising Utilization Over Time</h3>
                <p class="text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed">EV adoption is compounding. Properties that install today capture early users and build loyalty — meaning utilization (and revenue) grows year over year.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-evium-green/15 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-1">Passive by Design</h3>
                <p class="text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed">Evium manages everything — installation, software, maintenance, billing, and rebates. You collect revenue without managing operations.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-evium-green/15 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-2 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-1">Property Value Multiplier</h3>
                <p class="text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed">Charging infrastructure is increasingly expected by commercial tenants and residential buyers. Properties with EV charging command higher rents and better occupancy.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       REVENUE PROJECTION EXAMPLES
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="revenue-projection" class="py-28 bg-evium-dark">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-evium-green font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">By the Numbers</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black leading-tight mb-5">Revenue Projection Ranges</h2>
        <p class="text-white/55 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Based on real deployment data from Evium's NEVI-funded installations. Figures reflect a single 180kW DC Fast charger. Actual results vary by location, traffic, and pricing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <!-- Low utilization -->
        <div class="relative bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-white/20 rounded-t-2xl"></div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-white/40">Conservative</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mt-1">Low Utilization</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-white/10 pb-3">
              <span class="text-white/55 text-sm">Per month</span>
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">$900</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-white/10 pb-3">
              <span class="text-white/55 text-sm">Per year</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">$10,800</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
              <span class="text-white/55 text-sm">Over 5 years</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">$54,000</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-xs leading-relaxed">Approx. 8–12 sessions/day. Suitable for moderate-traffic lots with limited EV saturation today.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Medium utilization — featured -->
        <div class="relative bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-evium-green/40 overflow-hidden shadow-lg shadow-evium-green/5">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-evium-green rounded-t-2xl"></div>
          <div class="absolute top-5 right-5">
            <span class="bg-evium-green/15 text-evium-green text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-evium-green/30">Most Common</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-evium-green/70">Projected</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mt-1">Medium Utilization</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-white/10 pb-3">
              <span class="text-white/55 text-sm">Per month</span>
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-evium-green">$1,500</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-white/10 pb-3">
              <span class="text-white/55 text-sm">Per year</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-evium-green">$18,000</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
              <span class="text-white/55 text-sm">Over 5 years</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-evium-green">$90,000</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-xs leading-relaxed">Approx. 15–20 sessions/day. Represents the median across Evium's active deployment portfolio.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- High utilization -->
        <div class="relative bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-evium-green/60 rounded-t-2xl"></div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-white/40">Optimized</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mt-1">High Utilization</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-white/10 pb-3">
              <span class="text-white/55 text-sm">Per month</span>
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">$2,100</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-white/10 pb-3">
              <span class="text-white/55 text-sm">Per year</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">$25,200</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
              <span class="text-white/55 text-sm">Over 5 years</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">$126,000</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-xs leading-relaxed">Approx. 25–30 sessions/day. Achieved in high-traffic highway corridors and major commercial destinations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-white/30 text-xs">
        Figures are illustrative projections based on Evium NEVI deployment data for a single 180kW DC Fast charger. Revenue varies based on location, pricing strategy, and traffic volume. Multiple charger installations multiply revenue proportionally.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       HOW REVENUE IS CALCULATED
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-28 bg-evium-dark-light">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

        <!-- Formula visual -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-2xl p-10 border border-white/10">
          <p class="text-evium-green font-semibold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-8">The Revenue Formula</p>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-evium-green/10 border border-evium-green/20 flex items-center justify-center text-evium-green font-black text-lg flex-shrink-0">U</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-white">Utilization Rate</p>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">% of time the charger is actively in use. Grows with EV market share and property traffic.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-white/30 text-2xl font-light">×</div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-evium-green/10 border border-evium-green/20 flex items-center justify-center text-evium-green font-black text-lg flex-shrink-0">P</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-white">Session Price</p>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Per kWh or flat session rate. Set by owner or Evium — dynamic pricing available via software.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-white/30 text-2xl font-light">×</div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-evium-green/10 border border-evium-green/20 flex items-center justify-center text-evium-green font-black text-lg flex-shrink-0">V</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-white">Daily Volume</p>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Sessions per day, driven by site traffic, charger count, and visibility.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/10 flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-evium-green flex items-center justify-center text-evium-dark font-black text-lg flex-shrink-0">$</div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-white text-lg">Monthly Revenue</p>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Reported in real time via Evium's owner portal.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="text-evium-green font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">How It Works</p>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black leading-tight mb-6">
            Three levers. One clean revenue line.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Revenue is the product of how often the charger is used, what each session costs, and how many sessions happen each day. Evium's platform gives you visibility and control over each lever.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-white/60 text-base">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Dynamic pricing tools let you charge peak rates during high-demand periods and lower rates to incentivize off-peak usage.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Load management software prevents grid demand spikes and optimizes the number of concurrent sessions you can support.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Revenue reports, session logs, and station health data are available 24/7 in your owner portal.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       FINANCIAL MODEL COMPARISON
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-28 bg-evium-dark">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-evium-green font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Your Options</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black leading-tight mb-5">Choose Your Financial Model</h2>
        <p class="text-white/55 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Evium offers four distinct arrangements. The right model depends on your capital availability, risk tolerance, and revenue goals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

        <!-- No-Cost -->
        <div class="relative bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-evium-green/30 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 opacity-5" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, #2DC856, transparent 70%);"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-evium-green flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-evium-green/70">Zero Capital Required</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">No-Cost Model</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Evium covers 100% of equipment, installation, and operational costs. You provide the parking space. Evium retains ~90% of charging revenue; you receive ~10% as passive income. No investment, no liability — just returns.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-lg p-3">
              <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mb-1">Your capital outlay</p>
              <p class="text-white font-bold">$0</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-lg p-3">
              <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mb-1">Your revenue share</p>
              <p class="text-evium-green font-bold">~10%</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-xs">Best for: Property owners who want zero risk and zero overhead. Ideal first deployment or supplementary income.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Client Investment -->
        <div class="relative bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-white/40">Maximum Returns</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">Client Investment</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            You finance and own the equipment. You capture 100% of charging revenue. Evium handles rebate processing, installation, maintenance, and software — turning your capital investment into a high-yielding asset.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-lg p-3">
              <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mb-1">Your capital outlay</p>
              <p class="text-white font-bold">Variable</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-lg p-3">
              <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mb-1">Your revenue share</p>
              <p class="text-white font-bold">100%</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-xs">Best for: Owners with available capital who want full ownership and maximum long-term returns.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Hybrid -->
        <div class="relative bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-white/40">Flexible Terms</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">Hybrid Model</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
            A shared investment with proportional revenue split. You and Evium each contribute to capital costs, and revenue is divided according to agreed terms. Fully customized to your situation.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-lg p-3">
              <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mb-1">Your capital outlay</p>
              <p class="text-white font-bold">Shared</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-evium-dark rounded-lg p-3">
              <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mb-1">Your revenue share</p>
              <p class="text-white font-bold">Negotiated</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-xs">Best for: Portfolio operators who want a tailored arrangement across multiple properties or phased rollouts.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Leasing -->
        <div class="relative bg-evium-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
